<view class="message-page data-v-1ffa5f7a"><view class="hero-card data-v-1ffa5f7a"><view class="hero-badge data-v-1ffa5f7a">Message Center</view><text class="hero-title data-v-1ffa5f7a">把邀请、未读会话和最近沟通集中到同一个消息中心</text><text class="hero-desc data-v-1ffa5f7a"> 你可以先处理新的组队邀请，再进入具体聊天页查看组内消息和训练协同进度。 </text></view><view wx:if="{{a}}" class="section-card invite-card data-v-1ffa5f7a"><view class="section-head data-v-1ffa5f7a"><view class="data-v-1ffa5f7a"><text class="section-title data-v-1ffa5f7a">收到的邀请</text><text class="section-subtitle data-v-1ffa5f7a">先处理新的邀请，避免错过最近的组队机会</text></view></view><view class="invite-list data-v-1ffa5f7a"><view wx:for="{{b}}" wx:for-item="invite" wx:key="e" class="invite-item data-v-1ffa5f7a"><view class="invite-avatar data-v-1ffa5f7a">邀</view><view class="invite-content data-v-1ffa5f7a"><text class="invite-name data-v-1ffa5f7a">{{invite.a}}</text><text class="invite-desc data-v-1ffa5f7a"> 邀请你加入 {{invite.b}}</text></view><view class="invite-actions data-v-1ffa5f7a"><view class="invite-btn accept data-v-1ffa5f7a" catchtap="{{invite.c}}">接受</view><view class="invite-btn reject data-v-1ffa5f7a" catchtap="{{invite.d}}">拒绝</view></view></view></view></view><view wx:if="{{c}}" class="section-card data-v-1ffa5f7a"><view class="section-head data-v-1ffa5f7a"><view class="data-v-1ffa5f7a"><text class="section-title data-v-1ffa5f7a">会话列表</text><text class="section-subtitle data-v-1ffa5f7a">最近消息和未读状态会优先展示在这里</text></view></view><view class="message-list data-v-1ffa5f7a"><view wx:for="{{d}}" wx:for-item="group" wx:key="h" class="message-card data-v-1ffa5f7a" bindtap="{{group.i}}"><view class="group-avatar data-v-1ffa5f7a">组</view><view class="message-content data-v-1ffa5f7a"><view class="message-head data-v-1ffa5f7a"><text class="group-name data-v-1ffa5f7a">{{group.a}}</text><text wx:if="{{group.b}}" class="message-time data-v-1ffa5f7a">{{group.c}}</text></view><view class="message-preview data-v-1ffa5f7a"><text wx:if="{{group.d}}" class="message-text data-v-1ffa5f7a">{{group.e}}</text><text wx:else class="message-text empty data-v-1ffa5f7a">还没有聊天记录，进去发第一条消息吧。</text><view wx:if="{{group.f}}" class="unread-badge data-v-1ffa5f7a"><text class="unread-text data-v-1ffa5f7a">{{group.g}}</text></view></view></view></view></view></view><view wx:elif="{{e}}" class="empty-card data-v-1ffa5f7a"><view class="empty-icon data-v-1ffa5f7a">信</view><text class="empty-title data-v-1ffa5f7a">你还没有任何消息会话</text><text class="empty-desc data-v-1ffa5f7a">加入搭子组后，这里会展示邀请消息、未读会话和最近聊天记录。</text></view></view>